441,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"呢 d 叫火柴腳？！樓主係咪要驗下腦。"},{"pid":"f46228c64e06df0d954000923c565e6cc9691ae1","tid":251441,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"第二張圖邊算火柴"},{"pid":"7704ff72d139acd297c9cb2f245e04cf52544bdb","tid":251441,"uid":30487,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:56:19.000Z","msg":"大把肥婆小腿同大腿一樣粗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e252e3782f29d3fcb2c1cfee18408a8d3fd78fa5","tid":251441,"uid":116131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"火柴腳係麥撚野term <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過以事論事 呢種腳型<br />\n香港通街都係<br />\n不過係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論做office定地盤都有一大堆對腳瘦過碌撚既人<br />\n到底佢地細個係咪成日無飯食先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed5bb9ba6463aa58478a10e97ea7896977806b8","tid":251441,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二張圖邊算火柴</blockquote><br />\n我講緊個審美觀問題<br />\n至於你覺得第二張圖唔係火柴腳 你可以向廣告商反映一下唔夠火柴"},{"pid":"9176940dd6d59e3393ad7f9721ad5f88f48fa043","tid":251441,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"火柴腳係唔係潮流冇人知<br />\n但冇波就一定唔係"},{"pid":"84bd0383b789513790c198c00084bd35ff41130f","tid":251441,"uid":82572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"仲以為講男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二張點會火柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edb3510705a1cfe402cbd1cb51de9a6ee84fc