<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好核突"},{"pid":"cecc19a5ec251cedd0a6079db713692b3d681080","tid":251441,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲以為講男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二張點會火柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止我講架樓主</blockquote><br />\n個廣告話架喎<br />\n點解要入樓主數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你望下佢覆我咩 佢叫我同廣告商講唔夠火柴"},{"pid":"9604f3267c45ec34f0a8694f9f2afef74f89b305","tid":251441,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"第一個想屌"},{"pid":"2a459f03b6aced7c95b75ab9801dd0451dae65d9","tid":251441,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03a7ad410683a681627887718892b0f3fa621dab","tid":251441,"uid":6097,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲以為講男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二張點會火柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止我講架樓主</blockquote><br />\n其實我係cap句野 兩張圖都係<br />\n因為我覺得<br />\n「火柴腳係潮流」<br />\n「大腿同小腿要一樣細」<br />\n依兩句錯得好離譜<br />\n<br />\n唔係想同大家討論全智賢條腿係咪火柴腳<br />\n廣告商用佢張圖 可能求其搵 可能真係覺得係火柴腳<br />\n你覺得唔係 你可以同返佢講 張圖唔係我整<br />\n唔係我屈佢火柴腳<br />\n<br />\n我只係想表達我對嗰兩句嘅不滿<br />\n我認為一隻腳稱得上腳 要有線條<br />\n唔係好似火柴咁 更加唔係大腿跟小腿一樣細<br />\nOk嗎？"},{"pid":"49a932adf65e10f9aa07cb1b0add8ca348b73829","tid":251441,"uid":6097,"like":0,"d